nodes.text: The Taanab Spaceport was a major spaceport on the planet Taanab.

This spaceport was a scene of incident in 14 ABY when Disciples of Ragnos cultists released a mutated rancor into the complex. At this particular event, many cargo containers were destroyed by the mutated rancor before Jaden Korr was able to trap it in between a moving container and a force field in one of the loading docks, this way killing it.
